Exploratory data analysis

I am trying to judge the quality of my curves by plotting a line of g_s vs A/(c*(1+ VPD/D_0)). The notation is different, but is from equation 89 in the model-write-up of ED2. The Default value for c4 plants is 0.016, and can be found in the supplement. X in this code chunk referes to the result of A/ (c(1+ VPD/D_0)).

Note, it looks like VPD returned from the licore is in kPa and that the ratio is ED2 is mol w : mol. If I manually change D to two, I get a better looking graph.
